<h3><grey>Our</grey><orange> Objectives</orange></h3>
<br />
<div id="message">
<img src="../resources/images/learn.jpg" class="floatleft" alt="signboard" />
<h4><grey>Learn new algorithms and apply them in programming</grey></h4>
<p>With cOdErS your can learn new algorithms and prolblem solving techniques.You will be able to
better prepare yourself for competions and various exmas.</p>
</div>
<br />
<div id="message">
<img src="../resources/images/cafe.jpg" class="floatleft" alt="signboard" />
<h4><grey>Build up a problem solving community</grey></h4>
<p>cOdErS is also a problem solving community, to bring fellow programmers under one roof where they can discuss programming
related problems.
</p>
</div>
<br />
<hr />
<div id="message">
<img src="../resources/images/contest.jpg" class="floatleft" alt="signboard" />
<h4><grey>Organise online programming contests on regular basis</grey></h4>
<p>
At cOdErS we organise online programming contests on regular basis so that every one gets a fair chance to compete with others and test their skills and levels.
</p>
